{
  "stem": "22869.6",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a third floor where you could walk upon/ And they used to pull the nails out with the boards, and in between the ceiling and the floors they used to hide a lot of boxes.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wanted to dress up myself, so-- and I knew about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I took that axe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when she gave me the axe, she ran away from the house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She never came back, by the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She thought I was going to kill her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went up in the attic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I was really furious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I could have pulled all the nails and the boards out little by little and-- and make a decent job.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I took that axe, and I broke every piece of lumber there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I pulled out box by box of clothing that belonged to my sister that he had prepared for her-- for her wedding.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some bed sheets stuff.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We found boxes of soap.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A bar of soap after the war was like a piece of gold today, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I found my oldest brother's, Meyer's, suits, shirts, ties, all business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I took all these boxes, and I brought it down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time, my aunt came home already with her son.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can imagine how we were hugging and kissing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except she had very ill feeling towards me, which she told me later, because she felt that I was guilty that her husband was taken away by the mere fact--.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I was 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we went with these guys, every once in a while, they had an address.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every in a while, they would ask you, where does this guy live?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where does this guy live?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you understand?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
